00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:52.120
malicious intentions and dirty tricks.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:53.200
Otherwise,

00:02:54.880 --> 00:02:56.680
I will make you pay the price.

00:02:59.740 --> 00:03:00.430
Let's go.

00:03:09.020 --> 00:03:10.460
