there's a hidden connection among them.

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:33.540
I want you to help me verify it.

00:05:33.610 --> 00:05:35.810
You're so concerned about this matter.

00:05:35.970 --> 00:05:36.930
I assume

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:38.440
it's for your aunt, huh?

00:05:38.960 --> 00:05:40.220
You're so insightful.

00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:42.960
But you're not quite close to your aunt.

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:45.070
