00:06:00.220 --> 00:06:01.680
I'll definitely help you?

00:06:02.710 --> 00:06:04.370
Because you're soft-hearted

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:09.540
and can't bear
to see the weak people being bullied.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:10.800
I'm...

00:06:11.080 --> 00:06:12.100
soft-hearted?

00:06:37.850 --> 00:06:38.710
Your Highness.

00:06:39.770 --> 00:06:40.730
Go investigate

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:41.890
the clues
related to the loan sharking case.

00:06:41.890 --> 00:06:42.580
