00:09:21.350 --> 00:09:22.710
dry your tears

00:09:24.110 --> 00:09:25.590
and live well.

00:09:28.130 --> 00:09:30.400
My only regret is that

00:09:31.180 --> 00:09:33.520
I cannot stay with my Xi

00:09:34.330 --> 00:09:36.080
for a little longer.

00:09:38.550 --> 00:09:39.870
I don't expect

00:09:40.310 --> 00:09:43.230
you can
have great wealth or a high status.

00:09:44.970 --> 00:09:46.170
I only hope

00:09:48.080 --> 00:09:49.800
you can stay healthy

00:09:51.170 --> 00:09:53.700
and safe year after year.

00:09:57.910 --> 00:09:58.950
I will.

00:10:01.060 --> 00:10:02.570
I definitely will.

00:10:10.760 --> 00:10:12.640
Remember

00:10:13.160 --> 00:10:14.280
to keep

00:10:15.510 --> 00:10:16.950
this jade pendant well.

