are all determined by Heaven.

00:16:42.850 --> 00:16:44.120
What we can do as humans

00:16:45.020 --> 00:16:47.420
is to do our best
and strive for what we want.

00:16:51.930 --> 00:16:53.040
I believe

00:16:53.810 --> 00:16:56.270
